# Component conventions

- Server Components by default in app/; add "use client" only when the component needs state,
  effects, or browser APIs.
- One component per file, named export (no default exports).
- Props typed with an explicit `interface ComponentNameProps`, not inline object types for
  anything beyond 1-2 props.
- Co-locate: Component.tsx, Component.test.tsx, and (if applicable) Component.stories.tsx in
  the same folder.
- Don't put data-fetching inside a leaf presentational component — fetch in the feature's
  container/page and pass data down, or use the feature's own hook.
- Formatting/lint style is enforced by ESLint + Prettier — don't restate style rules here,
  `pnpm lint` is the source of truth.
